definitions.definition: Any of several passerine birds of the genera Quiscalus , Hypopyrrhus , Lampropsar and Macroagelaius , of the Americas , having iridescent plumage .
Any of several Asian myna birds of the genus Gracula .

main_definition: Any of several passerine birds of the genera Quiscalus , Hypopyrrhus , Lampropsar and Macroagelaius , of the Americas , having iridescent plumage .
secondary_definitions: ( loosely ) Any of several Asian myna birds of the genus Gracula .
